===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[wear]] something on the [[head]]; to [[carry]] on the head
#: {{zh-co|戴 帽子{zi}|to '''wear''' a hat}}
#: {{zh-x|踩 單車 要 戴 頭盔。|'''Put on''' a helmet when you ride a bike.|C}}
